com.marklogic.hub

Interface InstallInfo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    InstallInfoImpl

    public interface InstallInfo
    Stores and reports information from MarkLogic server about the installed status of the DHF This interface abstracts holding state. It does not make any calls itself.
